RWfPNx4gXsVE77-tJAzaK0hdROKqe7UJsZfm_-UjJ6O2ItW24CM3bxw ) ad nauseum, Apple=
 is, legally speaking, within its rights to collect whatever payments it wa=
nts from apps; that is why Rice=E2=80=99s thread is not a legal threat but =
an appeal to Apple=E2=80=99s better angels, as it were. These two tweets, t=
hough, offer what seems to me to be a compelling middle ground: creators be=
nefit from the investment of platforms like Fanhouse, and pay Fanhouse; Fan=
