Indeed, if we are to take Apple not by its word but by its actions, than th=
e conclusion that they are the truly abusive monopolist is hard to escape. =
This isn=E2=80=99t Apple monetizing its IP; it=E2=80=99s a tollkeeper colle=
cting rent just because it can.

Substack Next?
--------------

